query: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'movie' JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info > '7.0' JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('superhero', 'marvel-comics', 'based-on-comic', 'tv-special', 'fight', 'violence', 'magnet', 'web', 'claw', 'laser') JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name IS NOT NULL AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%' OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%') JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id

query: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM complete_cast AS cc JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'crew' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind <> 'complete+verified' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000 JOIN kind_type AS kt ON kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie', 'episode') JOIN movie_info_idx AS mi_idx ON t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.info < '8.5' JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mc.note NOT LIKE '%(USA)%' AND mc.note LIKE '%(200%)%' JOIN company_type AS ct ON ct.id = mc.company_type_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]' JOIN movie_keyword AS mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder', 'murder-in-title', 'blood', 'violence') JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Danish', 'Norwegian', 'German', 'USA', 'American') JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'
